--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^aspect
docTaxonomy
doc:
  Aspects model ontological relationships between definitions.
  See [Aspects]`docHaystack::Aspects` chapter.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^choice
is: [^aspect, ^symbol]
doc:
  Choice specifies an aspect with an single exclusive value.
  See [Aspects]`docHaystack::Aspects#choices` chapter.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^trait
is: [^aspect, ^list]
of: ^symbol
doc:
  Trait specifies a relationship between a def to zero or more defs.
  See [Aspects]`docHaystack::Aspects#traits` chapter.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^reciprocalOf
is: ^symbol
doc:
  Specifies the inverse of a trait relationship
  See [Aspects]`docHaystack::Aspects#reciprocalOf` chapter.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^is
is: ^trait
tagOn: ^def
doc:
  Defines one or more supertypes of a subtyping relationship.
  See [Subtyping]`docHaystack::Subtyping` chapter.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

