def: ^tagOn
is: ^trait
tagOn: ^def
reciprocalOf: ^tags
doc: "This tag is used on the given entity"
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^tags
is: ^trait
reciprocalOf: ^tagOn
computed
docSection
