--------------------------------------------------------------------------
def: ^containedBy
is: ^trait
tagOn: ^def
reciprocalOf: ^contains
doc:
  This entity is logically contained by the given entity. This
  trait is applied to ref tags that reference a parent entity.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
